      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING WATCH (5) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing third (22.28) and beaten 6 lengths over 390m at Warrnambool. Well-placed to take this out. SLICK ABILITY (1) goes very well this course and distance starting six times for two wins and three minors. Was out of the placings last time (24.62) at Bendigo in a Restricted WIN H, finishing seventh and beaten 3.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. PAW WELKES (4) is having his first look at this circuit. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 4.5 lengths (25.92) at Warrnambool. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Must be included in calculations. BIANCA'S SECRET (7) has not raced here but still warrants respect.",
